| Quantum Magic and Multi-Partite Entanglement in the Structure of Nuclei | Florian Brökemeier, S. Momme Hengstenberg, James W. T. Keeble, Caroline E. P. Robin, Federico Rocco, Martin J. Savage |   Motivated by the Gottesman-Knill theorem, we present a detailed study of the
