| Quantum-like nonlinear interferometry with frequency-engineered
  classical light | Romain Dalidet, Anthony Martin, Grégory Sauder, Laurent Labonté, Sébastien Tanzilli |   Quantum interferometry methods exploit quantum resources, such as photonic
entanglement, to enhance phase estimation beyond classical limits. Nonlinear
