| Linguini: A benchmark for language-agnostic linguistic reasoning | Eduardo Sánchez, Belen Alastruey, Christophe Ropers, Pontus Stenetorp, Mikel Artetxe, Marta R. Costa-jussà |   We propose a new benchmark to measure a language model's linguistic reasoning
