| Drifts of the sub-stellar points of the TRAPPIST-1 planets | Revol Alexandre, Émeline Bolmont, Mariana Sastre, Gabriel Tobie, Anne-Sophie Libert, Mathilde Kervazo, Sergi Blanco-Cuaresma |   Accurate modeling of tidal interactions is crucial for interpreting recent
