| Low Frame-rate Speech Codec: a Codec Designed for Fast High-quality
  Speech LLM Training and Inference | Edresson Casanova, Ryan Langman, Paarth Neekhara, Shehzeen Hussain, Jason Li, Subhankar Ghosh, Ante Jukić, Sang-gil Lee |   Large language models (LLMs) have significantly advanced audio processing
